refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;
database
The database resource, returned by dbase_open or dbase_create.

&reftitle.changelog;





    &Version;
    &Description;





    dbase 7.0.0

     database is now a resource
     instead of an int.

  &reftitle.examples;



    dbase_numfields Example


<?php

$rec = dbase_get_record($db, $recno);
$nf  = dbase_numfields($db);
for ($i = 0; $i < $nf; $i++) {
  echo $rec[$i], "\n";
}

?>
